  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Set yourself up for the day ahead with a good breakfast. You'll get a continental breakfast, with croissants, bread, jam, fruit, yoghurt and hot options like eggs.</p>
<p>For dinner you'll have a four-course meal starting with an antipasto buffet. You'll then get a choice of main, and to finish it off, a choice of local cheese and a pudding buffet. The ingredients used are all fresh and local and the food is traditional but with a modern twist. </p>
<p>If you're a wine lover, you have to check out the hotel's wine cellar, La Cantina,  which has over 450 kinds of Italian and international wine. You must try a wine from the Valtellina Valley while you're there!</p>]]></cateringDescription>
