  <description><![CDATA[<p>Located in the beautiful Italian Alps, the Hotel Lac Salin Spa &amp; Mountain Resort is perfectly geared up for cyclists, walkers and those of you wanting to relax in natural surroundings. It's the perfect retreat if you love action and relaxation. Named after the saltwater lake on Monte Livigno, the hotel focusses on embracing nature in everything they do- from the local produce used in their cooking to the herb-scented spa and wood panelled rooms. Every room has a balcony, so you can even enjoy nature from the comfort of your own room.</p>
<p>The staff do everything they can to help you get a feel for the region, with their free-guided walks and e-biking tours. They're very friendly and passionate about the area and are the best people to ask if you have any questions or need any local tips. It's easy to find something new to do every day, whether it's yoga, hiking, swimming or even torch-lit hikes! After a day of exploring, we love winding down in the spa's relaxation room. It's the best place to rest your mind and body. </p>
<p>Transfer time: approx. 3 hours by coach from Innsbruck airport.</p>
<p>Throughout September: transfers will go through St. Moritz and take approx. 3.5 hours</p>]]></description>
