  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Superior Sun Rooms </strong>are 28m² and sleep up to four people (the extra bed is a double sofa bed). They are bright and modern and have traditional Valtellina woven carpets. They have a minibar, balcony with deckchairs, TV, safe, bath or shower and hairdryer.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Rooms for Sole Use </strong>are also 28m² and have a balcony (from 6-19 Aug - only available on request).</p>
<p><strong>Deluxe Rooms </strong>are more spacious at 35m² and sleep up to four people. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>
<p><strong>Prestige rooms</strong> are 44m² and sleep up to four people. They have a king-size bed and a lounge area. The balcony has stunning mountain views. These rooms are available on request, please call to book. </p>]]></roomsDescription>
